        <item>
          <title>Cunningham and Harris help Pistons finish comeback for first playoff series win in 18 years</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Cade Cunningham had 32 points and 12 assists, Tobias Harris added 30 points and the Detroit Pistons beat the Orlando Magic 116-94 in Game 7 on Sunday to win a playoff series for the first time in 18 years.]]></description>
